      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POSH WHEELS (6) settled off speed and overcame a chequered run to work home into the placings when second (20.09) at this track in a Maiden. Has the ability and looks hard to top. JUST ON FIRE (4) settled well back early on debut and always towards the tail to finish sixth (23.33) at Geelong over 400m. Can do far better this time. VELVET LEGEND (2) is yet to break through in seven starts but has run a number of placings. Was below best latest when fourth (20.45) at this track but did hit the frame the start prior. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. REGAL REBA (8) is by My Redeemer out of Lawrie Road making debut. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can sneak into the frame with the right run.",
